title: Bug 121682: Exception is thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
description:
Description: When trying to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Open the report.
2. Navigate to the table containing the highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
OB: An exception is thrown in ReportEngineService.getMetaData() when trying to export data from the table containing the highlight/map.
EB: The data from the table containing the highlight/map should be successfully exported without any exceptions.
SR:
1. Open the report.
2. Navigate to the table containing the highlight/map.
3. Export the data from the table.
4. Verify that the data is successfully exported without any exceptions.
